description.en:
B2CCoin's aim is to be one of the most used payment methods when acquiring products and services; providing a simple and easy access to a valuable asset, by making a safe and reliable payment. It can be acquired, settled and used worldwide with no effort.

B2C is an established digital currency that allows individuals to make fast and secure transactions through a decentralised peer-to-peer network. It's digital cash and works without the need for bank or transfer fees. Supported by a large community of established and aspiring entrepreneurs, B2 coin has great potential for rapid growth and expansion.
